title: Crime Alert 03.28.19
itunes:title: Crime Alert 03.28.19
description:
Wisconsin prosecutor killed after driving her 5-year-old daughter to visit her grandparents. Jussie Smollett cleared of all charges related to the alleged hoax hate attack. Mom pleads guilty to drowning her 18-day-old son and suffocating two other infants in her care – and blaming it all on SIDS.
